There are 4 scenario in this programme.

signal : SIGINT(Ctrl+C)

<Scenario 1>
 * Register and set SIGINT do nothing
 * Ignore SIGINT

<Scenario 2>
 * Register and set SIGINT default behavior

<Scenario 3>
 * Register and set SIGINT using _exit(1) to exit

<Scenario 4>
 * Register and set SIGINT using function doSomething to handle
